name: The Fool
description: Welcome to social situations for introverts. Hats are mandatory, but we only have one type of hat available for you to wear. Please enjoy your stay. Once you enter, your hat might get a little heavy, because other guests like to attach decorations to the floppy ends. It's not a big deal. No, I didn't add that weight there. All I did was look at you. What do you mean it's getting too heavy? Are you really going to crawl at a party? Weirdo.
